{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"067922ca253a5870dc43468beb84433d","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Sessão N+1 — RQ-012 ✅ + FASE 0 RESEARCH COMPLETA\n\n**Commit:** `727b0314` — `research(akasha): RQ-012 — Sheldrake + Cymatics (12/12) Fase 0 COMPLETA`\n\n**Entregas:**\n- `.autonomous/research/systems/sheldrake-cymatics.md` (16k chars, 16 seções, 32+ fontes)\n- `.autonomous/research/chain-of-thought/cot-20260610-sheldrake-cymatics-position.md` (decisões)\n- INDEX + CHECKPOINT + feature_list.json + TODO.md + progress log atualizados\n\n**5 decisões Akasha (RQ-012):**\n1. Morphic fields = **metáfora pedagógica** (cita pró+contra white paper)\n2. Cymatics = **visual UX Pilar 4** (Chladni animado, Three.js Web Audio) — núcleo sólido Faraday 1831\n3. **NUNCA** afirma mecanismo físico (white paper \"O que Akasha NÃO afirma\")\n4. **I Ching ≠ frequências místicas** (Gene Keys evitou fusão, Akasha mantém)\n5. **Memetics (Dawkins 1976) > Morphic fields (Sheldrake 1981)** — Sheldrake = poesia, memetics = ciência\n\n**Fontes-chave citadas:** Sheldrake 1981/1999/2003/2012/2017/2020; criticas Maddox *Nature* 1981/1999, Wiseman 1998 PubMed 9734300, Shermer 2005 SAIC, Rose 1990, Skepdic 2025, Schmidt-Böbel 2004 BJP meta d=0.13; cymatics Chladni 1787, Faraday 1831, Jenny 1967 coined, Reid 2014 CymaScope, Park-Ji-Reid 2021 *WaterJournal*, McGowan 2017 ACM CymaSense, Codrops 2025, Cymatics Lab 2025-26; criticas 528Hz Horowitz/Science Feedback, 432Hz Calamassi-Pomponi 2019 n=33, Solfeggio Puleo 1970s.\n\n**Status projeto:**\n- 12/12 RQs (100%) — **Fase 0 (Research) COMPLETA**\n- ~12.5h research, $15 gastos, 12 commits\n- Próxima: **RQ-020 Patterns (Fase 1 — Synthesis)** — desbloqueado agora"}],"model":"MiniMax-M3","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"service_tier":"standard"},"service_tier":"standard","context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"17d0fd5a-6826-440d-a2ce-1aa3c